  "abstract": "Pigeonpea lines resistant to the causal agent of sterility mosaic did not permit continued multiplication of its eriophyid mite vector, Aceria cajani. Resistance to\r\nthe causal agent and lack -of continued multiplication of the mite vector on these lines are expected to provide greater stability of resistance to the disease....",
